ired-no-wifi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETin%20Can%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Seattle%20startup%20hawking%20these%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bdumb%20phones%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20I%20caved.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20didn't%20take%20much.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-teacher-shares-one-piece-of-advice-for-parents-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20married%20to%20a%20high%20school%20teacher%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20means%20I've%20had%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20the%20wreckage%20smartphones%20leave%20in%20adolescent%20brains.%20My%20husband's%20greatest%20hits%20include%20kids%20standing%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20in%20hallways%2C%20eyes%20glazed%2C%20typing%20away%20at%20each%20other%20instead%20of%20speaking.%20Add%20in%20the%20horror%20stories%20of%20online%20bullying%2C%20and%20I%20was%20sold.%20I%20made%20it%20through%20my%20entire%20school%20career%20without%20a%20smartphone%3B%20surely%20my%20son%20can%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20here's%20the%20other%20truth%3A%20I'm%20exhausted%20from%20being%20his%20social%20consigliere%2C%20the%20constant%20go-between%20who%20manages%20every%20sport-related%20text%2C%20every%20plan%2C%20every%20%26quot%3Bcan%20I%20call%20so-and-so%3F%26quot%3B%20By%20the%20time%20I%20was%20my%20son's%20age%2C%20I%20was%20not%20only%20using%20our%20family%20phone%20independently%2C%20but%20my%20parents%20had%20ingrained%20an%20entire%20script%20in%20my%20mind%20so%20as%20to%20answer%20appropriately%3A%20%26quot%3BLabberton's%20residence%2C%20this%20is%20Kinsey%20speaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20kid%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%3F%20With%20only%20the%20occasional%20experience%20of%20being%20passed%20a%20phone%20once%20the%20adults%20have%20handled%20the%20pleasantries%2C%20he's%20got%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-phone-ansewring-hello-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eall%20the%20telephone%20etiquette%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20a%20feral%20cat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271e47b1c-2681-4b87-a752-569707935134%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20wants%20independence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20craves%20independence.%20He%20wants%20the%20autonomy%20to%20make%20his%20own%20plans%2C%20and%20I%20want%20him%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20do%20so%20thoughtfully.%20So%20here%20we%20are%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bway%20back%20machine%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20device%20that%20looks%20exactly%20like%20what%20I%20used%20in%201992.%20And%20it's%20working.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20night%20I%20got%20his%20Tin%20Can%20up%20and%20running%2C%20my%20son%20was%20determined%20to%20call%20every%20friend%20he'd%20ever%20met.%20The%20problem%20was%2C%20dumb%20phones%20don't%20come%20with%20speed%20dial%20%E2%80%94%20or%20saved%20numbers%2C%20for%20that%20matter.%20So%20we%20went%20analog%20with%20the%20whole%20experience%3A%20pen%2C%20paper%2C%20and%20a%20handwritten%20roster%20of%20approved%20contacts%20(yes%2C%20I%20literally%20curated%20his%20social%20circle).%20Then%20I%20plugged%20the%20numbers%20into%20the%20Tin%20Can's%20companion%20app%2C%20which%20lets%20me%20control%20who%20he%20can%20and%20can't%20call.%20No%20mystery-number%20prank%20calls%20happening%20on%20my%20watch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENext%20came%20the%20bigger%20hurdle%3A%20what%20on%20earth%20to%20say%20once%20someone%20actually%20answered.%20Turns%20out%2C%20unlike%20me%2C%20my%20son%20had%20zero%20script.%20So%20there%20I%20was%2C%20suddenly%20channeling%20my%20own%20parents%3A%20Say%2C%20%26quot%3BHello%2C%20this%20is%20Wells.%20May%20I%20please%20speak%20to%20Charlie%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20coached%2C%20sounding%20every%20bit%20like%20the%20ghost%20of%20my%20parents'%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20his%20friend%20got%20on%20the%20line%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20my%20work%20here%20was%20done.%20Finally%20connected%2C%20I%20could%20merely%20look%20on%20with%20pleasure%20as%20my%20social%20butterfly%20caught%20up%20with%20one%20of%20his%20best%20buddies.%20Sure%2C%20they'd%20just%20hung%20out%20at%20school%20mere%20hours%20before%2C%20but%20the%20novelty%20of%20being%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20after%20hours%20on%20their%20own%20was%20intoxicating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210341d99-6df5-4b49-9a2e-d102448d7524%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20started%20organizing%20his%20own%20playdates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20my%20son%20descended%20the%20stairs%20with%20great%20authority%2C%20informing%20me%20that%20he'd%20taken%20the%20liberty%20of%20inviting%20a%20friend%20over.%20The%20playdate%2C%20he%20added%20matter-of-factly%2C%20would%20commence%20within%20the%20hour.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20slightly%20inconvenienced%20by%20the%20last-minute%20rendezvous%2C%20I%20bit%20my%20tongue.%20This%20was%20exactly%20what%20I'd%20hoped%20for.%20His%20excitement%20over%20the%20get-together%20he'd%20arranged%20pulled%20me%20back%20to%20my%20own%20childhood%2C%20when%20all%20that%20stood%20between%20me%20and%20a%20friend%20was%20a%20dial%20tone.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20what%20I%20want%20him%20to%20reach%20for%20when%20life%20gets%20hard%20or%20when%20he%20has%20joy%20to%20share.%20Not%20the%20flat%2C%20emoji-laden%20wasteland%20of%20digital%20chatter%2C%20shallow%20and%20distracting%20memes%2C%20or%20toxic%20online%20forums%2C%20but%20the%20breathless%20thrill%20of%20a%20friend's%20voice%20on%20the%20other%20end.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20this%20stripped-down%20phone%20can%20help%20him%20build%20that%20habit%20now%2C%20then%20consider%20us%20proof%20that%20sometimes%20less%20really%20dials%20up%20to%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERea