stems%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20it%20ourselves.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e49c4a54-dafd-4097-8194-5380bd537e48%5C%22%3E'Why%20do%20we%20have%20to%20say%20the%20names%20when%20the%20government%20knows%20the%20names%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20backtracked%20on%20earlier%20commitments%20to%20publish%20government%20documents%20about%20Epstein%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-federal-prison-camp-transfer-bryan-texas-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGhislaine%20Maxwell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20convicted%20in%202021%20of%20trafficking%20girls%20to%20Epstein%20for%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%20was%20permitted%20to%20plead%20guilty%20in%202008%20to%20minor%20prostitution%20solicitation%20charges%20in%20Florida%2C%20even%20though%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20collected%20evidence%20that%20the%20well-connected%20pedophile%20had%20sexually%20abused%20dozens%20of%20girls.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20killed%20himself%20in%20his%20Manhattan%20jail%20cell%20while%20awaiting%20trial%20for%20more%20severe%20sex-trafficking%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20summer%2C%20Maxwell%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-federal-prison-camp-transfer-bryan-texas-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20lax%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20serve%20the%20remainder%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-sentenced-20-years-prison-sex-trafficking-jeffrey-epstein-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E20-year%20sentence%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20giving%20an%20interview%20with%20Deputy%20Attorney%20General%20Todd%20Blanche.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-justice-department-interview-transcript-biggest-takeaways-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecordings%20of%20the%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20pu