0everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20two%20streaming%20services%2C%20including%20price%20and%20content%20comparisons%2C%20so%20you%20know%20which%20option%20might%20best%20suit%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22213be931-17b0-45d9-baa2-316fbe806c63%5C%22%3EPrices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EESPN%20Unlimited%20costs%20%2429.99%20a%20month%2C%20and%20Sling%20TV%20Orange%20costs%20%2445.99%20monthly.%20ESPN%20also%20has%20a%20cheaper%20%2411.99%20a%20month%20tier%2C%20ESPN%20Select%2C%20which%20offers%20everything%20from%20ESPN%20Plus%2C%20but%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20comparison%2C%20we'll%20be%20evaluating%20the%20full%20Unlimited%20plan.%20Similarly%2C%20Sling%20has%20add-ons%20and%20a%20Sling%20Orange%20%2B%20Blue%20combination%20plan%20for%20%2460.99%20a%20month%2C%20but%20we'll%20be%20exclusively%20looking%20at%20the%20base%20Orange%20plan%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESling%20Orange%20also%20offers%20a%20five-month%20%26quot%3BSeason%20Pass%26quot%3B%20for%20%24199%2C%20and%20ESPN%20Unlimited%20has%20an%20annual%20plan%20for%20%24299.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESling%20also%20recently%20introduced%20short-term%20passes%20beyond%20the%20standard%20month-to-month%20option%20for%20its%20Orange%20plan.%20Customers%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20day%20pass%20(%244.99)%2C%20weekend%20pass%20(%249.99)%2C%20or%20weeklong%20pass%20(%2414.99).%20However%2C%20the%20Walt%20Disney%20Company%2C%20which%20owns%20ESPN%2C%20is%20suing%20Sling%20TV%20over%20the%20passes%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2025%2F08%2Fdisney-sues-sling-tv-mini-bundles-violate-carriage-deal-terms-1236498333%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeadline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eaa64188-3b82-4d38-8282-8523ffb4ca6c%5C%22%3EChannels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ESPN%20Unlimited%20lineup%20includes%20ESPN%2C%20ESPN2%2C%20ESPN3%2C%20ESPNU%2C%20ESPNews%2C%20SEC%20Network%2C%20SEC%20Network%20Plus%2C%20ACC%20Network%2C%20ACC%20Network%20Extra%2C%20and%20everything%20on%20ESPN%20Plus%20and%20ESPN%20on%20ABC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ESPN%20streaming%20service%20is%20also%20the%20home%20of%20UFC.%20Major%20numbered%20UFC%20events%2C%20featuring%20marquee%20title%20fights%2C%20require%20a%20%2479.99%20pay-per-view%20(PPV)%20fee%20for%20each%20event%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20subscription%20to%20ESPN%20Select%20or%20above.%20However%2C%20UFC%20rights%20in%20the%20US%20will%20switch%20to%20Paramount%20Plus%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESling%20Orange%20carries%2030%2B%20channels%2C%20including%20ESPN%2C%20ESPN2%2C%20ESPN3%2C%20and%20ESPN4K.%20The%20plan%20also%20carries%20networks%20like%20Disney%20Channel%2C%20TNT%2C%20CNN%2C%20AMC%2C%20and%20TBS.%20While%20Sling%20Orange%20doesn't%20carry%20ABC%2C%20we've%20found%20that%20many%20ESPN%20on%20ABC%20games%20are%20available%20to%20live%20stream%20through%20the%20ESPN3%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESling%20also%20offers%20customers%20the%20option%20to%20purchase%20extra%20channel%20packages%20for%20an%20additional%20monthly%20fee%2C%20like%20Sports%20Extra%20for%20%2411%20a%20month.%20Through%20the%20Orange%20plan%2C%20Sports%20Extra%20unlocks%20channels%20including%20the%20ACC%20Network%2C%20EPSNU%2C%20ESPNews%2C%20SEC%20Network%2C%20SEC%20Network%2B%2C%20MLB%20Network%2C%20MLB%20Network%20Strike%20Zone%2C%20Tennis%20Channel%2C%20NBA%20TV%2C%20NHL%20Network%2C%20and%20beIN%20Sports.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fsling-tv-channels%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESling%20TV%20channels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2297c88d2d-b0a1-4e4b-877f-09c21a6daef3%5C%22%3EApp%20experience%20and%20user%20interface%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20you%20open%20the%20two%20apps%20on%20a%20laptop%20or%20TV%2C%20you're%20prompted%20with%20content%20that%20might%20be%20of%20interest.%20This%20could%20be%20anything%20from%20events%20or%20shows%20you've%20recently%20watched%20to%20the%20top%20program%20currently%20available%20on%20the%20app%2C%20especially%20if%20there's%20an%20ongoing%20major%20event%20like%20the%20US%20Open.%20Both%20apps%20also%20have%20a%20search%20function%20to%20allow%20viewers%20to%20look%20directly%20for%20their%20desired%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESling%20TV%20is%20a%20standard%20live%20TV%20streaming%20app%2C%20with%20a%20clear%20TV%20guide%2C%20and%20On%20Demand%20and%20DVR%20sections.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20few%20extra%20app%20perks%2C%20like%20scores%20for%20ongoing%20or%20recent%20sporting%20events.%20It's%20at%20times%20bare%20bones%20and%20could%20benefit%20from%20having%20programming%20tiles%20like%20its%20peers%20(Fubo%2C%20for%20one)%2C%20but%20it%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20and%20is%20immediately%20usable%20with%20no%20major%20learning%20curves%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20simplicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222842%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sling%20TV%20guide%20showing%20ESPN%2C%20ESPN2%2C%20and%20ESPN3%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b065edcfc04e97619c3188%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221374%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESling%20TV%20guide%3Cp%3ESling%20TV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EESPN%20Unlimited%20is%20just%20an%20enhanced%20version%20of%20the%20ESPN%20app%2C%20so%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20news%20articles%2C%20recap%20clips%2C%20and%20scores%20available%20as%20well%2C%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20streaming%20account.%20Getting%20to%20the%20streaming%20portion%20of%20the%20app%20involves%20clicking%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BWatch%26quot%3B%20section%20of%20the%20site%20or%20app.%20However%2C%20having%20everything%20from%20ESPN%20in%20one%20place%2C%20including%20news%20and%20streaming%20options%2C%20makes%20for%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20crowded%20app%2C%20especially%20as%20you're%20learning%20the%20ropes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20more%20straightforward