ies%2C%20one%20alarming%20pattern%20cut%20across%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalence%20of%20child%20marriage%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20teenage%20pregnancy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20field%20assessments%20by%20his%20team%20revealed%20an%20even%20more%20disturbing%20pattern%3A%20girls%20as%20young%20as%2013%20were%20giving%20birth.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20health%20emergency%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20humanitarian%20and%20developmental%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20young%20girls%20were%20losing%20their%20futures%20before%20they%20even%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20act%20now%2C%20our%20demographic%20dividend%20will%20become%20a%20demographic%20burden.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jaiswal%2C%20the%20concern%20ran%20deeper%20than%20numbers.%20As%20a%20doctor%2C%20he%20had%20studied%20how%20child%20marriage%20fuels%20a%20cycle%20of%20malnutrition%2C%20infant%20mortality%2C%20and%20poor%20maternal%20health.%20He%20had%20also%20seen%20how%20cultural%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20like%20women%20eating%20last%20in%20the%20household%20%E2%80%94%20weakened%20nutrition%20for%20mothers%20and%20children%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reflects%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20see%20a%20child%2C%20barely%20a%20teenager%2C%20bearing%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20motherhood%20is%20unsettling.%20It%20deprives%20her%20of%20opportunities%2C%20and%20it%20deprives%20society%20of%20her%20potential.%20We%20needed%20a%20district-specific%20response%2C%20something%20bold%20and%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20ground%20reality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20that%20urgency%20in%20mind%2C%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Sankalp%E2%80%99%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%