orce%20conducts%20a%20final%20review%20before%20declaring%20a%20village%20eligible%20for%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20rigour%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20villages%20is%20being%20monitored%20in%20phases%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20certifying%20all%20169%20Gram%20Panchayats%20(GPs)%20and%20Village%20Committees%20(VCs)%20across%20Sepahijala.%20Since%20the%20mission%20began%2C%20more%20than%20100%20children%20have%20already%20been%20rescued%20from%20early%20marriage%2C%20with%20rehabilitation%20support%20underway%20to%20help%20them%20rebuild%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20picture%20is%20also%20shifting%3A%20health%20facilities%20reporting%20zero%20deliveries%20among%20under-18%20girls%20have%20risen%20from%20four%20in%20December%202024%20to%2011%20by%20March%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202027%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20hopes%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriage%20in%20Sepahijala%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20three%20years%20ahead%20of%20the%20global%20target%20under%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goal%205.3.%20%E2%80%9CMission%20Sankalp%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20another%20initiative%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaiswal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20personal.%20It%E2%80%99s%20urgent.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20safeguarding%20our%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Sepahijala%20district%20administration.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756872000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ftripura-child-marriages-prevention-4-1756816819.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D495335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20happens%20when%20one%20district%20decides%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20let%20its%20daughters%20become%20child%20brides%3F%20In%20Sepahijala%2C%20IAS%20officer%20Siddharth%20Jaiswal%E2%80%99s%20mission%20has%20already%20saved%20100%20children%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20rallying%20entire%20villages.%22%2C%22a