ity%2C%20and%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roshan%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPiyushi%20Taunk%2C%20Head%20of%20Department%20at%20Echoes%20of%20Earth%2C%20elaborates%3A%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20piece%20is%20handcrafted%20and%20tested.%20We%20build%20prototypes%2C%20run%20safety%20checks%20with%20engineers%2C%20and%20embed%20R%26amp%3BD%20at%20every%20stage%20%E2%80%94%20from%20non-toxic%20finishes%20to%20load-bearing%20analysis.%20The%20result%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20stage%2C%20but%20an%20installation%20that%20tells%20stories%20and%20sparks%20conversations%20about%20sustainability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20waste%20into%20art%20and%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaste%20is%20often%20the%20Achilles%E2%80%99%20heel%20of%20festivals%20%E2%80%94%20but%20here%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20triumph.%20From%20its%20first%20edition%2C%20Echoes%20of%20Earth%20has%20been%20%3Cstrong%3E100%25%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F430285%2Fsix-ways-to-cut-down-on-waste-during-your-summer-vacation-earth-day%2F%5C%22%3Eplastic-free%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20No%20bottled%20water%2C%20no%20disposable%20cutlery.%20Instead%2C%20RO%20water%20filters%20supply%20clean%20water%20and%20festival-goers%20carry%20steel%20tumblers%2C%20bought%20on%20entry%20and%20refundable%20at%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXfGEIhiw2PoIuYJZ8nTpDAs_u4oB53a7nC08rp1yhiOuebtndPtxiLv1xlqRoijMbusV84yjXQ7F8nLTSCVQTKNu4kljQIri3VYMDX_B73KsOqhWadWCc9x3rR1x1KjEa_WxVoVaw%3Fkey%3Dys9ALPWqixXprY3KoP9cPg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20dustbins%20scattered%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roshan%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20there%20are%20%E2%80%98Kiosk%C2%A0stations%E2%80%99%20where%20volunteers%20guide%20attendees%20to